These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish
City: colone, marseilles
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Pet       | goldfish       | bird |
| City         | marseilles | colone  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, house
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, lettuce
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
3. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre           | dubstep | house      |
| Food   | lettuce  | cucumber      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, prince
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Cigar          | montecristo    | prince   |
| Sport   | biathlon  | rowing   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

