.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, climbing
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, red
1. the person who likes green is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Sport      | baseball       | climbing |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Job           | security-guard | nurse    |
| Color   | green           | red   |

