The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, country
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, coach
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, brazilian
1. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
2. the coach is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | video-games   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | country       |
| Job         | designer   | coach |
| Nationality     | brazilian    | chinese     |

