.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
2 different games are played: poker, canasta
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, superhero
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, aquamarine
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person who likes azure is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Game           | canasta | poker     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime          | superhero |
| Color           | azure          | aquamarine    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 